|Examples={{Example
|Example.Language=Spanish
|Example.Text=Los géneros creados por la televisión en México, musicales o de humor, dramáticos o noticiosos, parecerían, para alimentar teorías conspirativas, diseñados, creados e implementados desde hace mucho con el propósito de idiotizar al grueso de una población a la que paulatinamente se ha ido orillando al peldaño siguiente en una siempre descendiente escalera socioeconómica: la clase alta se volvió media, la media popular, la popular simplemente pobre y la inmensa mayoría de gente pobre se volvió miserable por millones.
|Example.Gloss=The genres created by the television in Mexico musical or of humor drama or news appears to feed theories conspiratorial designed created and implemented since ago much with the goal of make-idiots to-the thick of a population to which that slowly refl has been forcing to-the rung next in an always descending ladder socioeconomic the class high refl turns middle the middle popular the popular simply poor and the immense majority of people poor refl turn miserable by millions.
|Example.English translation=The genres of Mexican television, musical or comedy, drama or news, seems--to feed conspiracy theories--designed, created, and implemented since long ago with the goal of making idiots out of the bulk of a population that has been slowly forced down to the next rung in an always-descending socioeconomic ladder: the upper class becomes middle, the middle becomes working class, the working class simply poor, and the vast majority of poor people become miserable by the millions.
|Example.Provenance=http://www.jornada.unam.mx/2012/11/18/sem-moch.html
|Example.Comments=orillando al peldaño siguiente en una siempre descendiente escalera socioeconómica
